1. *Pali* se vatromet (It is shooting off fireworks). 
2. Svi su se okupili da *pale* sveće (Everyone gathered to light candles). 
3. U kući je *palila* žarulja (The house was turning on the lightbulb).
4. *Pali* se svijeća za uspomenu (A candle is lit in memory). 
5. *Palo* je nebo u vatru (The sky was on fire).